Trinity::

She looked up at BH, "What? You don't know what you did? You shot me, 
and it hurt a bunch.  I don't like getting shot.  And you tried to 
hurt my friends.  I don't want you to hurt my friends.  OK?"  She 
walked up to him and put her small paw on his foot. "Now don't make 
me get roudy, it's not a pretty sight." Her paw barely covered what 
would be classified as his toes. She crained her neck straight up to 
look at him. "Now, are you going to behave or what?"
